    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Models that illustrate the construction process or construction phases of a built work or ship; an example would be a model illustrating support systems that will be hidden by walls and roofing.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
